storyline: Akai Ito Story  This summer I lost my motherthe only family I had left I took a long train ride to see my family home which I inherited from my father I had a strange dreama red memory I was unable to recall There was a kaleidoscope of shining blue butterflies flying about and a familiar person with sad eyes My birthplace Hemidzuka It is there I will meet someone and there I will part from someone Past and present dream and reality my memories and my blood The threads of fate will intertwine and twist together to form a single picture The wheel of fate is about to turn  Aoi Shiro Story  My grandmother who passed away long ago loved to travel Strange landscapes Unfamiliar people She loved meeting new people She would say those raised under a high ceiling will grow tallerand seeing the world makes a person bigger During the summer vacation of my second year in high school I too went on a trip far away It was a training camp for extracurricular activities but it was by no mistake a trip By train and car we headed to the southern sea With our swords and gi packed we headed to teh temple gate of the cape overlooking Oniga Island It was there I met The waxing and waning of the moon the ebb and flow of the tides the cycle of destiny that disturbs the surface of the water I will resist the storm brought about by the dragon who slumbers within the azure shrine

summary: Hello Goodboy  a cozy and wholesome narrative adventure game about finding the purpose of your journey in the afterlife together with a huggable cute doggo  Play as Iko a kid new to the afterlife without a memory of their past trying to find the purpose of their journey in this place You will be accompanied by Coco a cute and huggable dog that will help solve the mysteries and will always be by your side  In Hello Goodboy you will meet various souls on their own adventures through the afterlife experience heartwarming stories from them that are full of kind messages help their problems by clearing lightweight challenges and enjoy time with delicious food together There are several paths to the end to find the purpose of your journey but the choices and time are limited so decide well how you will spend your time with
storyline: Arriving in the afterlife with no memory a kid trying to unravel the mysteries and mend mistakes from the forgotten past life accompanied by a good boy doggo  Meet Iko a lost soul who just arrived in the afterlife with no memory intact In the confusion state Coco a mysterious dog appears to help and guide Iko to start the adventure in this place called Kuruto Without knowing what will come at the end Iko reassures to continue and unravel the mysteries ahead  Iko and Cocos journey will be full of choices Choosing one will bring consequences and leave the unknown behind Iko should always follow what the heart says and Coco will always be there by the side With Magic Hourglass and Magic Toolbox has given Iko will meet and befriend various denizens in the afterlife Listening to their unique story and helping them deal with problems will give Iko a meaningful purpose as the glimpse of past memory reappears  Good and bad things might be happening in this adventure But worry not Coco will always be there for Iko Spend the time well enjoy the adventure together and dont forget to give Coco a ton of hugs and belly rubs  Hello Goodboy features   Wholesome experience Heartwarming and meaningful stories in all parts of the game   Series of meaningful choices Every choice is different and will alter the ending Multiple endings await   Beautiful art and music Fully handdrawn art and heartful crafted music will soothe the eyes and ears while the story does the magic to the heart   Coco the good boy The best friend ever And yes you can interact with the dog such as hug it and give a belly rub
